comment: Gasol (SAS) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Bledsoe (PHO) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Tucker (PHO) makes incidental body to body contact with Leonard (SAS).
Booker (PHO) makes incidental contact with Leonard (SAS) that does not affect his SQBR.
Chandler (PHO) sets the screen on Parker (SAS) and makes leg to leg contact that affects his ability to defend the play.
Gasol (SAS) makes body to body contact with Booker (PHO) that affects his SQBR.
Booker (PHO) makes incidental contact with Ginobili (SAS) that does not affect his SQBR.
There is no clear and conclusive video evidence that Tucker (PHO) cleanly blocks the shot attempt by Leonard (SAS).
Parker (SAS) briefly engages with Booker (PHO) off ball.
Aldridge (SAS) and Chandler (PHO) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Booker (PHO) legally contests Green's (SAS) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Green (SAS) makes marginal contact with Tucker's (PHO) arm that does not affect his SQBR.
Leonard (SAS) commits a take foul on Tucker (PHO).
Bender (PHO) makes contact with Gasol (SAS) that affects his SQBR.
Dedmon (SAS) makes incidental contact with Bender (PHO) that does not affect his SQBR.
